The pricing model of curve is a little different from that of uniswap ,it usually gives you a better yield that uniswap
because of the pricing model that has been implemented by curve. Its very preferred for the trade of stablecoins .
Curve does the pricing by actually using a very complex equation for the conversion of one token to another 
